body:
#### PR description:

This PR addresses part of an issue from (https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/40765).

In this PR:
* Introdukujc of new record - TotemAnalysisMaskRcd - separated from TotemReadoutRcd;
* Serialization of records and inner classes intended to be placed in the CondDB;
* Writer plugin and config for reading XML files and placing objects in SQLite;
* Updates of printer plugin which prints records content;


#### PR validation:

Validation has been made with use of new plugin which reads data from SQLite/XML file and drops them to text file. 
All data from XML was dropped to SQLite in separate records and with different IOVs.
Then (using new plugin) objects were read from SQLite and dropped to text file.
Also data from XML files was read and dropped to other text file.
Then files were compared and their content was the same, as expected.
